ee how thats a bad thing.  I gain weight easy and have a hard time loosing it my metabolism wants to hold everything. I'm just the opposite. I've always been thin. I guess my metabolism is just high. I don't have a lot of muscle either. I've tried to bulk up, but I just can't. ",test_426_2
