t driving can't. it's just something different to experience the terrain with different viewpoints and landmarks, lakes and rivers, it's really soothing. as well as great exercise! Since I do tend to eat a lot of food too being a chef and all. too many desserts sometimes there have been bears or cougars nearby, but thankfully not close enough for me to come into contact with. i carry bear spray with me just in case. always prepared! do you know if there are good hiking trails near where you live?",test_506_3
