My favorite spicy food is tofu drunken noodles. I like the spicy chicken sandwiches at Burger King. I like any spicy food. I work at McDonald's. I work at McDonald's. I dress in a Hamburglar costume at work. I work at the drive through. I do not get paid to dress as Hamburglar. I was arrested last month at McDonald's. I feel solidarity with other fast food workers.,"I love spicy tofu drunken noodles. Do you like spicy food too? Of course, I really like the spicy chicken sandwich at Burger King. Burger King is the best,  I could eat it every night. I'm a big lover of food too. I like just about anything spicy. I need to try the chicken sandwich at BK. It's weird that I like Burger King so much because I work at McDonald's, but I just can't help myslef. I actually work at McDonald's right now too. They don't have a good spicy option for me.  What job do you do at McDonald's? I dress up as the Hamburglar and steal fries from all the little kids' happy meals. Lol. I wish I had that job. I actually work the drive through. Not to exciting.  Not at all! We are all a little weird in the fast food business.  I'm glad to hear you say that. Are you busy next Wednesday? There was  a police thing at a McDonald's last month and I got arrested. I could really use a character witness. I will be there. I would protect any of my fast food brothers and sisters. ",test_551_2
