"I found a local place for diving lessons. I have been saving for a trip to Hawaii. I want to have my first dive there. I have an ex wife. I have done dives in Hawaii. I am going to Hawaii this fall. I should be able to go to Hawaii in a month. I will move to Hawaii next year if I can find a house. I have money coming from my ex. We can go diving in Hawaii. I have snakes and dogs. I would like to be on the beach. I might get a condo. My pets names are Slinky, Nagini, Bean, and Boris.","I actually just made a couple of calls and I found a local place where I can take diving lessons.  I'm so exccited! I've been trying to save up the money for a trip to Hawaii. I would love to have my first dive there! I have done a few dives in Hawaii and all have been great.  In fact, the only thing I didn't like was that my ex-wife was along as well!  lol.  Any idea when you will be going?  I plan on going back this fall for 2 weeks. I should be able to go in about a month! im so excited because I've heard it is so beautiful. It is.  I plan on looking for a house while I am there.  If I can find something I like I will move there next year.   Oh thats so cool. Maybe I can vacation in Hawaii and we can hang out for a while? Sure.  We will have to go diving of course.  I am going to look at my options on all the islands.  Since I have some money coming from my ex-wife, I should be able to afford something nice.   I would love to get something on the beach, but that may be a bit out of my price range.  I was going to look at condos, but I want a place I can take my pets - both my snakes and my dogs.",test_556_3
